***(ABSTRACT)
*
*        THIS MODIFICATION COMBINES THE JOB HELD AND JOB-ON-READER MESSAGES.
*         THIS ( SLIGHTLY ) REDUCES THE NUMBER OF CONSOLE MESSAGES, BUT
*         THE PRIMARY FUNCTION IS TO OFFSET THE 'HELD' MESSAGE ACROSS
*         THE CONSOLE TO MAKE IT MORE OBVIOUS TO THE LOCAL OPERATORS.
*
*        ( UNDER HASP 3.1 THIS WAS MODIFICATION NUMBER 'M035' ).
